EN: He walks every day to play basketball.

ZH: 我们打算明天一起走路去山上爬山。
EN: We plan to walk together to hike up the mountain tomorrow.

ZH: 她走路去图书馆借书。
EN: She walks to the library to borrow books.

ZH: 他每天都会走路去公园溜狗。
EN: He walks to the park every day to walk the dog.

ZH: 我们要小心走路，路很滑。
EN: We need to walk carefully, the road is slippery.

ZH: 走路是锻炼身体的好方法。
EN: Walking is a good way to exercise.
